Class RegistryNetByteBuf

java.lang.Object
io.netty.buffer.ByteBuf
net.minecraft.network.PacketByteBuf

com.kneelawk.knet.api.util.RegistryNetByteBuf
All Implemented Interfaces:
NetBuf<NetByteBuf>, io.netty.buffer.ByteBufConvertible, io.netty.util.ReferenceCounted, Comparable<io.netty.buffer.ByteBuf>
public class RegistryNetByteBuf extends NetByteBuf
A NetByteBuf bound to a particular DynamicRegistryManager instance. This buffer is like a NetRegistryByteBuf except it extends NetByteBuf instead of RegistryByteBuf.

Class hierarchy: 

               PacketByteBuf
                 /         \
   RegistryByteBuf      NetByteBuf
              |               |
 NetRegistryByteBuf<->RegistryNetByteBuf
